<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Georg Erkensteiner</head><p>Der Rat teilt die Abwesenheit des Peter Eytenholzer, Bürger zu Nürnberg, mit, und erklärt sich nach Rückkehr und Forderung zu dessen Befragung über die angeblichen Verdächtigungen des Adressaten wegen der Beschlagnahme zweier Pferde zu Neustadt an der Aisch bereit.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_61" id="29v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_61_r1l1">Görgen Erkenſteiner </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_61_r1l2"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Görg als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt vvıe eẅch <expan>fürkom<ex>en</ex></expan> ſey daʒ eın <expan>vnſ<ex>err</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_61_r1l3"><expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> / dem ʒu der Neẅnſtat ʒwey pferd <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> ſınd . <expan>argenwıll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_61_r1l4">ʒu eẅch trage etc das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> / vnd nachdem als wır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_61_r1l5">erfarn <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſo trıft dıe ſache <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Eytenholcʒ<ex>er</ex></expan> an den <expan>hett<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_61_r1l6">wır beſant vnd <expan>wolte<ex>n</ex></expan> mıt Jm <expan>dauo<ex>n</ex></expan> geredt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . ſo ıſt er auf dıſʒ ʒeıt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_61_r1l7">nıht anheim <expan>geweſ<ex>en</ex></expan> / VVenn er <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> herheım kombt / ſo <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> mıt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_61_r1l8">Jm <expan>dauo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>rede<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd eẅch eın antwurt <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> tun ob wır daran gemant </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_61_r1l9"><expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> / Denn wo wır eẅch lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> vȷ<hi rend="sup">a</hi></ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_61" id="29v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Görgen Erkensteiner </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Görg, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt, wie ewch
                                <expan>fürkom<ex>en</ex></expan> sey, daz ein
                            <expan>uns<ex>err</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, dem zu der Newnstat zwey pferd
                                <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> sind,
                            <expan>argenwill<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> zu ewch trage etc., das
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>.
                        Und nachdem als wir erfarn <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, so trift die sache
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>
<expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Eytenholcz<ex>er</ex></expan> an, den <expan>hett<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        wir besant und <expan>wolte<ex>n</ex></expan> mit im
                            <expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan> geredt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, so
                        ist er auf disz zeit niht anheim <expan>gewes<ex>en</ex></expan>. Wenn er
                                <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> herheim kombt, so
                            <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> mit im
                                <expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>rede<ex>n</ex></expan> und ewch ein antwurt
                            <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> tun, ob wir daran gemant
                                <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>. Denn wo wir ewch lieb
                                <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst etc.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> vi<hi rend="sup">a</hi>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
